    <section class="faqs-a">
    <div class="w-overlay"></div>
    <div class="s-wrap">
        <h3 class="text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-12">
                    <div class="ft_content">
                        <div class="tab-content" id="faq-tab-content">
                            <div class="tab-pane show active" id="tab1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab1">
                                <div class="accordion" id="accordion-tab-1">
                                    <div class="card ft_card">
                                        <div class="card-header ft_crd_hdr" id="accordion-tab-1-heading-1">
                                            <h5>
                                                <button class="btn btn-link ft_ac_btn" type="button"
                                                    data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#accordion-tab-1-content-1"
                                                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-tab-1-content-1">What is SEO Service?</button>
                                            </h5>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="collapse" id="accordion-tab-1-content-1"
                                            aria-labelledby="accordion-tab-1-heading-1" data-parent="#accordion-tab-1">
                                            <div class="card-body">
                                                <p>Search Engine Optimization or SEO service is the most convenient and result-driven digital marketing activity. It helps your website gain desired exposure and visibility, builds trust and visibility. It also drives conversions by improving Google search rankings, drives organic traffic, increases engagement, and increase returns on investment.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>


                                    <div class="card ft_card">
                                        <div class="card-header ft_crd_hdr" id="accordion-tab-1-heading-2">
                                            <h5>
                                                <button class="btn btn-link ft_ac_btn" type="button"
                                                    data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#accordion-tab-1-content-2"
                                                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-tab-1-content-2">What is a Backlink in SEO?</button>
                                            </h5>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="collapse" id="accordion-tab-1-content-2"
                                            aria-labelledby="accordion-tab-1-heading-2" data-parent="#accordion-tab-1">
                                            <div class="card-body">
                                                <p>When you start to learn SEO, one of the words you will hear often is backlinks or incoming links. Yes, backlinks play an important role in SEO and ranking specially when it comes to Google and any search engine. Search engines consider these backlinks as votes for your site and contents which will eventually improve your site’s ranking in the search results page. Backlinks are not so easy to get, but we will help you enjoy a higher level of Google trust.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="card ft_card">
                                        <div class="card-header ft_crd_hdr" id="accordion-tab-1-heading-3">
                                            <h5>
                                                <button class="btn btn-link ft_ac_btn" type="button"
                                                    data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#accordion-tab-1-content-3"
                                                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-tab-1-content-3">Why SEO is important for the website?</button>
                                            </h5>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="collapse" id="accordion-tab-1-content-3"
                                            aria-labelledby="accordion-tab-1-heading-3" data-parent="#accordion-tab-1">
                                            <div class="card-body">
                                                <p>SEO is important for the website because Search engine optimization is to get your website rankings in major search engines for relevant phrases and keywords. An SEO (Search Engine Optimizer) is the one who optimizes the site as to enhance the traffic. SEO brings the consumer to the website to produce leads, sales etc. It’s like blood in a body. For that reason, SEO is important for the website and help website owners in achieving a higher rank.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="card ft_card">
                                        <div class="card-header ft_crd_hdr" id="accordion-tab-1-heading-4">
                                            <h5>
                                                <button class="btn btn-link ft_ac_btn" type="button"
                                                    data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#accordion-tab-1-content-4"
                                                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-tab-1-content-4">Are custom SEO packages available?</button>
